                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;The documentation of &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.python.org/3/library/functions.html#locals&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;locals()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; specifically says: &quot;The contents of this dictionary should &lt;b&gt;not&lt;/b&gt; be modified.&quot; (emphasis mine)&lt;/span&gt;

