            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This does not work with &lt;code&gt;__dict__&lt;/code&gt; variable however. I wonder if there is a general mechanism to create &lt;i&gt;any&lt;/i&gt; global variable dynamically.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/898649/alexey&quot; title=&quot;3,543 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Alexey&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment84051166_46897025&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2018-01-30 18:25:02Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Jan 30, 2018 at 18:25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;globals()&lt;/code&gt; can do this&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/5823489/guillaume-lebreton&quot; title=&quot;2,129 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Guillaume Lebreton&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment84068764_46897025&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2018-01-31 07:42:21Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Jan 31, 2018 at 7:42&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
